track_notes: Ascent starts at Rossfall bus stop on the Urnaesch-Schwaegalp line. Descent ends at Urnaesch train station. There is a restaurant right in the activation zone (closed in winter).
Popular trail that follows the road to the summit, but in winter it is covered with snow, but still relatively easy.
Snowshoe/winter hike, therefore not always exactly on the hiking trails.
